import pandas as pd
import os

fdir='c:/py_data/주유소/'
fname=os.listdir(fdir)

df0=pd.DataFrame()

for fn in fname:
    try: 
        df1=pd.read_excel(fdir+fn, header=2)
        df0=pd.concat([df0, df1], ignore_index=True)
    except:
        continue
    
del df1, fn
df0.info()

In [10]:
lat=[]
lng=[]

for sch in df0['주소']:
    ggmap=gmaps.geocode(sch, language='ko')
    lat.append(ggmap[-1]['geometry']['location']['lat'])
    lng.append(ggmap[-1]['geometry']['location']['lng'])
    
df0['위도']=lat
df0['경도']=lng
display(df0.head(3))

[미션] folium으로 상위/하위 10개씩 각각 색 표시 다르게 지도에 원표시 해보자¶

  • 참고: https://xeros.dev/142
In [277]:
import folium

center = [37.522073773256515, 126.98434690968251]


df1 = df1.sort_values(by='휘발유')

high10 = df1.tail(10)
low10 = df1.head(10)

m = folium.Map(location = center, zoom_start = 10)

for md in high10.index:
    folium.CircleMarker([df1.loc[md, '위도'], df1.loc[md, '경도']]
                       , radius = 15, color = '#CD3181'
                       , fill_color = '#CD3181'
                       , popup = df1.loc[md, '상호']).add_to(m)

for md in low10.index:
    folium.CircleMarker([df1.loc[md, '위도'], df1.loc[md, '경도']]
                       , radius = 15, color = '#3186cc'
                       , fill_color = "#3186cc"
                       , popup = df1.loc[md, '상호']).add_to(m)
    
m.save("c:/users/yong/desktop/tmp/서울주유소_상위_하위_10.html")
